- Programming languages: (fill in as appropriate, e.g., Python, JavaScript)
- IoT Integration: Connect real or simulated sensors and actuators.
- Visualization: Dashboard/web interface to monitor and control.
- Data Analysis: Predictive algorithms for maintenance and optimization.

